+ Intro

Guess who it is? Yeah, that's right. It's me: [[*user winkwonkboi]], back at it again with some more doodles. This time, it's SCiPTEMBER, and I'm about to draw my hand out.

This'll be where I store all my annual doodles for this year (2022) and possibly the years after that. I might not be able to do all prompts since I don't have all the time in the world, but I'll be sure to make up for it eventually.

Anyways, here's some eye candy:
